Analysis

Overview

This analysis uses CPR case data from the ZOLL to evaluate code blue response efficiency. The data was collected from the SICU High Performance Code Team binder, and there are 24 CPR cases ranging from 2020-01-11 to 2020-12-26. The primary goals of this PACE project are to:

  • Establish a code blue performance baseline
  • Gain insight to what areas of CPR techniques are lacking
  • Educate fellow staff members
